name: bMath
tagline: A simple math game for baby
body:
### Welcome to bMath
This is an experimental app for a gaming platform for babies.

```
$ writed in objective-C
$ extended with cocos2X
$ designed with cocos builder
```

### Status
The project is in it's first round... so if you want you can try it but it's very poor
